12
00:02:08,460 --> 00:02:09,300
Let us finish praying!

13
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:10,700
I still need to bow three times.

14
00:02:10,700 --> 00:02:11,460
Come back later.

15
00:02:11,460 --> 00:02:12,060
Bow three times.

16
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:13,660
Pan Xiao!

17
00:02:14,940 --> 00:02:15,700
