21
00:02:20,580 --> 00:02:21,340
Come on, let's go again.

22
00:02:22,260 --> 00:02:22,860
Let's go back.

23
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,580
Come on.

24
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:24,380
Let's get another shot.

25
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:26,260
- No. - No way.

26
00:02:26,660 --> 00:02:27,540
Just one more.

27
00:02:28,260 --> 00:02:28,860
Help us out.

28
00:02:29,060 --> 00:02:30,020
What do you take me for?

29
00:02:30,180 --> 00:02:31,660
You think you can use me whenever you feel like it?

30
00:02:31,660 --> 00:02:32,300
Let's go, Teaty.

31
00:02:32,460 --> 00:02:33,080
Pen.

32
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:35,580
That's a good line.

33
00:02:37,060 --> 00:02:39,140
Think you can use me

34
00:02:40,020 --> 00:02:41,820
